alid registry entries. You can check for the following registry entries: Help files, Fonts, Shortcuts, Startup, Start Menu, Shared files, Application Paths, File Associations, History records, Sound Files, COM &amp; ActiveX entries.\n[/extra_wrap]\n[/custom_element]\n\n[/span12]\n\n[row]\n\nimage-9\n\n[span12]\n<h3>Shredder - Secure erase files and folders</h3>\n[hr]\n[/span12]\n\n[/row]\n\n[span12]\n\n[custom_element element=\"div\" css_class=\"custom_img\" inner_wrapper=\"false\"]\n\n[frame align=\"left\"]<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-2073\" title=\"Shredder - Secure erase files and folders\" src=\"http://localhost/bodrag/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/shredder.jpg\" alt=\"Shredder - Secure erase files and folders\" width=\"204\" height=\"150\" />[/frame]\n\n[extra_wrap]\nDo you have files that contain important information and need to be deleted? Then you should not simply delete them by using the Recycle Bin! Because this data can be restored by other users of your computer. You cand delete files and foders, safe and unrecoverable, using the Shredder application and nobody can recover your data.\n[/extra_wrap]\n[/custom_element]\n\n[/span12]\n\n[row]\n\nimage-10\n\n[span12]\n<h3>Disk Wipe - Secure erase free space on your hard disk</h3>\n[hr]\n[/span12]\n\n[/row]\n\n[span12]\n\n[custom_element element=\"div\" css_class=\"custom_img\" inner_wrapper=\"false\"]\n\n[frame align=\"right\"]<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-2073\" title=\"Disk Wipe - Secure erase free space on your hard disk\" src=\"http://localhost/bodrag/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/diskwipe.jpg\" alt=\"Disk Wipe - Secure erase free space on your hard disk\" width=\"204\" height=\"150\" />[/frame]\n\n[extra_wrap]\nDid you simply deleted files with important information? Anyone can see them by using file recovery software.To make sure that your confidential information are gone forever you should secure erase your hard disk free space, using Disk Wipe application and nobody can recover them using data recovery software.\n[/extra_wrap]\n[/custom_element]\n\n[/span12]\n\n[row]\n\nimage-11\n\n[span12]\n<h3>Startup Security - Monitors all applications which start with Windows</h3>\n[hr]\n[/span12]\n\n[/row]\n\n[span12]\n\n[custom_element element=\"div\" css_class=\"custom_img\" inner_wrapper=\"false\"]\n\n[frame align=\"left\"]<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-2073\" title=\"Startup Security - Monitors all applications which start with Windows\" src=\"http://localhost/bodrag/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/startupsecurity.jpg\" alt=\"Startup Security - Monitors all applications which start with Windows\" width=\"127\" height=\"150\" />[/frame]\n\n[extra_wrap]\nMany applications launch automatically when Windows start without asking for your permission. With Startup Security you can monitor all startup applications and you can choose which are allowed and which should be blocked.\n[/extra_wrap]\n[/custom_element]\n\n[/span12]\n[row]\n\nimage-12\n\n[span12]\n<h3>Computer Security - Protects your online privacy</h3>\n[hr]\n[/span12]\n\n[/row]\n\n[span12]\n\n[custom_element element=\"div\" css_class=\"custom_img\" inner_wrapper=\"false\"]\n\n[frame align=\"right\"]<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-2073\" title=\"Computer Security - Protects your online privacy\" src=\"http://localhost/bodrag/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/computersecurity.jpg\" alt=\"Computer Security - Protects your online privacy\" width=\"204\" height=\"150\" />[/frame]\n\n[extra_wrap]\nHow important is your privacy? While surfing the Internet, for example, the content of web pages is stored in your browsers cache . Cookies, browsing history, passwords are also stored on your computer for later use . Windows stores links to to recent used documents and applications, temporary files that may contain confidential information.\nWould you like to erease all these traces? The <strong>Computer Security</strong> tool from Bodrag Utilities is the right choice for you.\n\n[/extra_wrap]\n[/custom_element]\n\n[/span12]\n[row]\n\nimage-13\n\n[span12]\n<h3>EXE Protector - Password protection for your executable files</h3>\n[hr]\n[/span12]\n\n[/row]\n\n[span12]\n\n[custom_element element=\"div\" css_class=\"custom_img\" inner_wrapper=\"false\"]\n\n[frame align=\"left\"]<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-2073\" title=\"EXE Protector - Password protection for your executable files\" src=\"http://localhost/bodrag/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/exeprotector.jpg\" alt=\"EXE Protector - Password protection for your executable files\" width=\"204\" height=\"150\" />[/frame]\n\n[extra_wrap]\nIf your computer is used by several people and there are applications that you want to restrict to be used by foreign users, then EXE Protector will help you to do so. With EXE Protector you can protect any application with a password, and that application can run only when entering the correct password.\n\n[/extra_wrap]\n[/custom_element]\n\n[/span12]\n\n[row]\n\nimage-14\n\n[span12]\n<h3>Spyware Protector - Protect your computer against mallware products installation</h3>\n[hr]\n[/span12]\n\n[/row]\n\n[span12]\n\n[custom_element element=\"div\" css_class=\"custom_img\" inner_wrapper=\"false\"]\n\n[frame align=\"right\"]<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-2073\" title=\"Spyware Protector - Protect your computer against mallware products installation\" src=\"http://localhost/bodrag/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/spywareprotector.jpg\" alt=\"Spyware Protector - Protect your computer against mallware products installation\" width=\"212\" height=\"150\" />[/frame]\n\n[extra_wrap]\nSpyware, adware, browser hijackers, and dialers are some of the most annoying and dangerous threats on the Internet today. By simply browsing a web page, you could find your computer infected by one of these unwanted fiends! Spyware Protector can help you to keep your system secure. But, unlike other programs, Spyware Protector does not scan your system for spyware. It will secure your system in order to protect it to be infected when you visit webpages.\n<strong>Spyware Protector</strong> can help you keep your system secure.\n\n[/extra_wrap]\n[/custom_element]\n\n[/span12]\n\n[row]\n\nimage-15\n\n[span12]\n<h3>Registry Backup - Created backup of Registry files for the Recovery</h3>\n[hr]\n[/span12]\n\n[/row]\n\n[span12]\n\n[custom_element element=\"div\" css_class=\"custom_img\" inner_wrapper=\"false\"]\n\n[frame align=\"left\"]<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-2073\" title=\"Registry Backup - Created backup of Registry files for the Recovery\" src=\"http://localhost/bodrag/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/registrybackup.jpg\" alt=\"Registry Backup - Created backup of Registry files for the Recovery\" width=\"159\" height=\"150\" />[/frame]\n\n[extra_wrap]\nThe registry file is an important component of your system. If it is destroyed, your operating system will run with errors or in the worst case, it will no longer run. To prevent this, we recommend to backup your registry records. Basically, you should do it prior to any registry change. With Registry Backup you can create registry backups and restore them.\n[/extra_wrap]\n[/custom_element]\n\n[/span12]\n\n[row]\n\nimage-16\n\n[span12]\n<h3>Process Manager - Manages your current running applications</h3>\n[hr]\n[/span12]\n\n[/row]\n\n[span12]\n\n[custom_element element=\"div\" css_class=\"custom_img\" inner_wrapper=\"false\"]\n\n[frame align=\"right\"]<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-2073\" title=\"Process Manager - Manages your current running applications\" src=\"http://localhost/bodrag/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/processmanager.jpg\" alt=\"Process Manager - Manages your current running applications\" width=\"133\" height=\"150\" />[/frame]\n\n[extra_wrap]\nDo you know exactly what applications are currently running on your system? With Process Manager from Bodrag Utilities you get now all needed details. It displays all running applications, all processes and their memory requirements and computer performance graphics.\n[/extra_wrap]\n[/custom_element]\n\n[/span12]\n\n[row]\n\nimage-17\n\n[span12]\n<h3>Startup Manager - Manages the list of applications which start with Windows</h3>\n[hr]\n[/span12]\n\n[/row]\n\n[span12]\n\n[custom_element element=\"div\" css_class=\"custom_img\" inner_wrapper=\"false\"]\n\n[frame align=\"left\"]<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-2073\" title=\"Startup Manager - Manages the list of applications which start with Windows\" src=\"http://localhost/bodrag/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/startupmanager.jpg\" alt=\"Startup Manager - Manages the list of applications which start with Windows\" width=\"197\" height=\"150\" />[/frame]\n\n[extra_wrap]\nMany applications launch automatically when Windows start. Some of them are required, for example to provide you with important functions such as your virus scanner. Others are useless or even dangerous applications that also start together with your system. Any new application that is added to Windows startup will make your system to start more slowly and have less free memory.\nWith the Startup Manager from Bodrag Utilities you can now manage applications that launch on Windows startup.\n\n[/extra_wrap]\n[/custom_element]\n\n[/span12]\n\n[row]\n\nimage-18\n\n[span12]\n<h3>Service Manager - Manages the list of installed Windows services</h3>\n[hr]\n[/span12]\n\n[/row]\n\n[span12]\n\n[custom_element element=\"div\" css_class=\"custom_img\" inner_wrapper=\"false\"]\n\n[frame align=\"right\"]<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-2073\" title=\"Service Manager - Manages the list of installed Windows services\" src=\"http://localhost/bodrag/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/servicemanager.jpg\" alt=\"Service Manager - Manages the list of installed Windows services\" width=\"160\" height=\"150\" />[/frame]\n\n[extra_wrap]\nYou have installed applications that run as service and you want to stop it? Or you want to change the way it start? You can use Service Manager to make all these and also to get details about each installed service on your system.\n[/extra_wrap]\n[/custom_element]\n\n[/span12]\n\n[row]\n\nimage-19\n\n[span12]\n<h3>Uninstaller - Manages your installed applications</h3>\n[hr]\n[/span12]\n\n[/row]\n\n[span12]\n\n[custom_element element=\"div\" css_class=\"custom_img\" inner_wrapper=\"false\"]\n\n[frame align=\"left\"]<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-2073\" title=\"Uninstaller - Manages your installed applications\" src=\"http://localhost/bodrag/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/uninstller.jpg\" alt=\"Uninstaller - Manages your installed applications\" width=\"173\" height=\"150\" />[/frame]\n\n[extra_wrap]\nDuring the use of your computer you will install some applications. If you don\'t need an application anymore, you can uninstall it and clean it from your system. Also, you can edit uninstall entries for your applications and see which applications have invalid uninstall entries.\n[/extra_wrap]\n[/custom_element]\n\n[/span12]\n\n[row]\n\nimage-20\n\n[span12]\n<h3>System Information - Displays extended information about your system and hardware</h3>\n[hr]\n[/span12]\n\n[/row]\n\n[span12]\n\n[custom_element element=\"div\" css_class=\"custom_img\" inner_wrapper=\"false\"]\n\n[frame align=\"right\"]<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-2073\" title=\"System Information - Displays extended information about your system and hardware\" src=\"http://localhost/bodrag/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/systeminformation.jpg\" alt=\"System Information - Displays extended information about your system and hardware\" width=\"208\" height=\"150\" />[/frame]\n\n[extra_wrap]\nDo you know exactly what hardware is installed in your system, the version number of your operating system, or what Internet connections are installed? With System Information from Bodrag Utilities ther is no longer a secret for you! You can get detailed information about your entire system.\n[/extra_wrap]\n[/custom_element]\n\n[/span12]\n\n[row]\n\nimage-21\n\n[span12]\n<h3>Windows Styler - Customize your Windows interface</h3>\n[hr]\n[/span12]\n\n[/row]\n\n[span12]\n\n[custom_element element=\"div\" css_class=\"custom_img\" inner_wrapper=\"false\"]\n\n[frame align=\"left\"]<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-2073\" title=\"Windows Styler - Customize your Windows interface\" src=\"http://localhost/bodrag/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/windowsstyler.jpg\" alt=\"Windows Styler - Customize your Windows interface\" width=\"213\" height=\"150\" />[/frame]\n\n[extra_wrap]\nDo you like default icons of Windows? Would you prefer different icons for your files &amp; folders? Then you can use Windows Styler from Bodrag Utilities to make these changes.\n[/extra_wrap]\n[/custom_element]\n\n[/span12]\n\n[row]\n\nimage-22\n\n[span12]\n<h3>Wallpaper Changer - Changes your desktop wallpaper automatically</h3>\n[hr]\n[/span12]\n\n[/row]\n\n[span12]\n\n[custom_element element=\"div\" css_class=\"custom_img\" inner_wrapper=\"false\"]\n\n[frame align=\"right\"]<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-2073\" title=\"Wallpaper Changer - Changes your desktop wallpaper automatically\" src=\"http://localhost/bodrag/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/wallpaperchanger.jpg\" alt=\"Wallpaper Changer - Changes your desktop wallpaper automatically\" width=\"147\" height=\"150\" />[/frame]\n\n[extra_wrap]\nYou might have lots of beautiful pictures on your computer that can make your desktop look awesome, but you have to manually change your wallpaper. Bring life to your desktop with Wallpaper Changer from Bodrag Utilities. It changes your desktop wallpaper automatically. Of course, you select which background images should be displayed.\n[/extra_wrap]\n[/custom_element]\n\n[/span12]\n\n[row]\n\nimage-23\n\n[span12]\n<h3>Auto Shutdown - Schedule when your computer must shut down</h3>\n[hr]\n[/span12]\n\n[/row]\n\n[span12]\n\n[custom_element element=\"div\" css_class=\"custom_img\" inner_wrapper=\"false\"]\n\n[frame align=\"left\"]<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-2073\" title=\"Auto Shutdown - Schedule when your computer must shut down\" src=\"http://localhost/bodrag/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/autoshutdown.jpg\" alt=\"Auto Shutdown - Schedule when your computer must shut down\" width=\"171\" height=\"150\" />[/frame]\n\n[extra_wrap]\nThis application lets your computer automatically shutdown. This is especially useful if you run an application with a task, that will take a long time to run, and you don\'t have the time to stand and wait until you can shut down the computer.\nInstead of shutting down the computer, you can also choose to restart, logo off, go in standby mode or hibernate.\n\n[/extra_wrap]\n[/custom_element]\n\n[/span12]\n[row]\n\nimage-24\n\n[span12]\n<h3>Tweaker - Customize your Windows settings</h3>\n[hr]\n[/span12]\n\n[/row]\n\n[span12]\n\n[custom_element element=\"div\" css_class=\"custom_img\" inner_wrapper=\"false\"]\n\n[frame align=\"right\"]<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-2073\" title=\"Tweaker - Customize your Windows settings\" src=\"http://localhost/bodrag/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/tweaker.jpg\" alt=\"Tweaker - Customize your Windows settings\" width=\"194\" height=\"150\" />[/frame]\n\n[extra_wrap]\nIf you wan to customize your system settings, Tweaker is the perfect choice.In this way, you can make the operating system more effective and tailored to meet your needs.\n[/extra_wrap]\n[/custom_element]\n\n[/span12]\n\n\n\n<div id=\"download\" class=\"download\" style=\"height:10px;\"></div>\n&nbsp;\n[row]\n\n[span12]\n<h2>Downloads</h2>\n[hr]\n[/span12]\n[/row]\n\n[row]\n[span12]\n[extra_wrap]\n<h3>Bodrag Utilities</h3>\n<b>General Information</b>\n<strong>Version:</strong>          <span>1.10</span>\n<strong>Release date:</strong>     <span>November 30, 2010</span>\n<strong>Trial period:</strong>     <span>30 days</span>\n<strong>Platform:</strong>         <span>Windows 98, Me, 2000, XP, Vista, Windows 7</span>\n<strong>Languages:</strong>       <span>English</span>\n[/extra_wrap]\n[/spa