ecurely erases hard disks free space to make sure that old deleted documents are impossible to be recovered.\n&nbsp;\n<strong>Protecting</strong>\nBodrag Utilities monitors all applications at start-up and lets you know about possible sneaky ones.\nIt protects your online privacy based on Bodrag`s previous successful Wipe Expert application and also password protects your executables in order to prevent faulty use. It prevents installation of spyware to make sure your PC behaviour is not watched and also creates registry backups in order for you to maintain a stable system.\n&nbsp;\n<strong>Fixing and repairing</strong>\nBodrag Utilities manages:\n<ul>\n<ul>\n	<li>your list of running applications</li>\n</ul>\n</ul>\n\n<ul>\n<ul>\n	<li>your list of start-up applications</li>\n</ul>\n</ul>\n\n<ul>\n<ul>\n	<li>your list of Windows services</li>\n</ul>\n</ul>\n\n<ul>\n<ul>\n	<li>uninstalling of your applications</li>\n</ul>\n</ul>\n<strong>More Features: </strong>\n<ul>\n<ul>\n	<li>Bodrag Utilities provides advanced details about your system and hardware</li>\n</ul>\n</ul>\n\n<ul>\n<ul>\n	<li>It helps customize your Windows interface and settings, helps change the desktop background</li>\n</ul>\n</ul>\n\n<ul>\n<ul>\n	<li>It is also able to schedule events like shut downs, sleep, and hibernate status</li>\n</ul>\n</ul>\n<strong>Supported Windows versions</strong>\nThe software supports Windows XP and Windows Vista and Windows 7 (32-bit versions).\n&nbsp;\n<strong>Price and availability</strong>\nBodrag Utilities can be purchased for $44.95 via download at <a href=\"http://localhost/bodrag/downloads/bodrag-utilities\">www.bodrag.com</a>\n&nbsp;\n<strong>About Bodrag </strong>\n<strong>Bodrag</strong> is a dynamic IT company with 100% U.S.A capital. It was established in 2004, in Nashua, NH. <strong>Bodrag</strong> was founded as a software development company. Bodrag is known for its award winning Windows products: Outlook Express Backup Expert, Wipe Expert, Foxmail Backup Expert and, the latest addition to the product portfolio, a RAM Booster Expert.\n', 'Bodrag Software Delivers Complete, Fast and Easy PC Optimization with Bodrag Utilities', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'bodrag-software-delivers-complete-fast-and-easy-pc-optimization-with-bodrag-utilities', '', '', '2015-09-02 17:23:50', '2015-09-02 17:23:50', '', '0', 'http://localhost/bodrag/?p=2373', '0', 'post', '', '0'), ('2378', '1', '2015-09-02 17:31:04', '2015-09-02 17:31:04', '', 'news01', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', 'news01', '', '', '2015-09-02 17:31:04', '2015-09-02 17:31:04', '', '2373', 'http://localhost/bodrag/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/news01.png', '0', 'attachment', 'image/png', '0'), ('2379', '1', '2015-09-02 17:32:12', '2015-09-02 17:32:12', '<strong>Nashua, NH</strong><strong> - </strong>Bodrag Software announced today the availability of their RAM Booster Expert  an easy to use and powerful memory optimizer tool that boosts computer performance and makes Windows run much faster and more stable.\n\nRAM Booster Experts main feature is memory de-fragmentation. This is extremely useful as many software products, including Windows, load into memory a large amount of libraries that are not constantly used, creating memory blocks. The RAM Boost Expert from Bodrag finds these blocks and unloads them to a page file. When some of this data becomes necessary, it is loaded back to the RAM.\n\nThe software also operates when applications close: occasionally, not the entire allocated memory is released and RAM Booster Expert finds these memory leaks and flushes them, increasing the size of free memory.\n\nOptimization processes can be scheduled to run when the user is away from the computer. The application shows detailed information about physical memory (total, free and used), page file (total, free and used), clipboard content and CPU usage. This information is displayed in text and graphical mode.\n\nAlso, the RAM Booster Expert is supplied with two other useful tools: Process and Startup Manager. The Process Manager allows the user to view detailed information about running processes and to stop them if necessary. The Startup Manager helps the user view and delete applications that start on Windows startup.\n\nRAM Booster Expert 1.00 can be bought online from Bodrags website, at <a  href=\"http://www.bodrag.com/\">http://www.bodrag.com</a>. The price of a single copy is $24.95 Dollars.\n\nClick here to download your free evaluation copy of <a href=\"http://localhost/bodrag/product/ram-booster-expert\">RAM Booster Expert</a>\n\n<strong>About Bodrag</strong>\nBodrag Software is a software development company, known for its award winning Windows products: Outlook Express Backup Expert, Wipe Expert, Foxmail Backup Expert and, the latest addition to the product portfolio, a RAM Booster Expert.\nThe company was founded in 2004 and is headqartered in Nashua, NH.\nMore information about Bodrag can be found at www.bodrag.com.', 'RAM Booster Expert makes Windows run faster and more stable', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'ram-booster-expert-makes-windows-run-faster-and-more-stable', '', '', '2015-09-02 17:32:12', '2015-09-02 17:32:12', '', '0', 'http://localhost/bodrag/?p=2379', '0', 'post', '', '0'), ('2383', '1', '2015-09-02 17:39:39', '2015-09-02 17:39:39', '[posts_list thumbs=\"normal\" post_content=\"excerpt\" order_by=\"date\" order=\"DESC\" link=\"yes\" tags=\"yes\"]', 'News', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'news', '', '', '2015-09-02 17:39:39', '2015-09-02 17:39:39', '', '0', 'http://localhost/bodrag/?page_id=2383', '0', 'page', '', '0'), ('2389', '1', '2015-09-02 23:15:11', '2015-09-02 23:15:11', ' ', '', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', '2389', '', '', '2015-09-02 23:15:11', '2015-09-02 23:15:11', '', '0', 'http://localhost/bodrag/2015/09/02/2389/', '1', 'nav_menu_item', '', '0'), ('2390', '1', '2015-09-02 23:15:11', '2015-09-02 23:15:11', ' ', '', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', '2390', '', '', '2015-0